==============================
How to set tax-included prices
==============================

Tax-included price
==================

If you want your sales prices to be tax-included (B2C), check *Included in Price* for your sales taxes in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`.

.. image:: media/tax_included.png
   :align: center

You can rely on following documentation if you need both tax-included (B2C) and tax-excluded prices (B2B): :doc:`B2B_B2C`.

Show tax-included prices in eCommerce catalog
============================================
By default prices displayed in your eCommerce catalog are tax-excluded. To display it in tax-included, check *Show line subtotals with taxes included (B2C)* in :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration --> Settings` (Tax Display).

